    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1205710096">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1205710096" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1205710096" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1205710096">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/54738756/">谙冉</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-06-22</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">拿书的时候很怕故事的沉重，很怕历史浅薄的我读起来会艰难，但是从开始阅读这一些都已抛之脑后。难以想象作者当时如何用如此冷静、不带仇恨的笔触写下他的经历。作者仿若一个旁观者却把读者们带入到情境当中去。翻译也很赞。好书</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1202780570">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1202780570" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1202780570" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1202780570">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
